 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the fan of disco is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person eating strawberry and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
16. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing whist##1
